	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "067f8727-51a8-44e6-be13-b222e2e41c58",
		"name": "Domain API (v2 - Refactored)",
		"description": "API collection for Domain Management.\n\n### Base URL\n`http://127.0.0.1:8002/api`\n\n### Roles:\n- **Superadmin**: admin@example.com / password\n- **Manager**: manager@example.com / password\n- **Employee**: employee@example.com / password\n\n### Domain Response Fields:\n- `system_status` — Auto-calculated from expiry_date (Active, Expiring soon, Pending Renewal, Renewal in Progress, Expired)\n- `manual_status` — Manually set by user (e.g., On Hold, Cancelled)\n- `days_to_expiry` — Integer, negative if expired\n- `priority` — Critical / High / Medium / Low\n- `payment_summary` — `{ total_amount, total_paid, balance_pending }`\n- `sales_person` — Full user object\n- `branch` — Full branch object\n- `renewed_by` — Full user object",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
